# VHS Demo — supply-chain-mcp-server
Output .github/demo.gif

Set Shell "bash"
Set FontSize 14
Set Width 900
Set Height 550
Set Theme "Catppuccin Mocha"
Set Padding 20
Set TypingSpeed 35ms

# Show help
Type `npx supply-chain-mcp-server --help`
Sleep 300ms
Enter
Sleep 5s

# List all tools
Type `npx supply-chain-mcp-server --list`
Sleep 300ms
Enter
Sleep 5s

# Run a tool
Type `npx supply-chain-mcp-server --tool epss_score '{"cve_id":"CVE-2024-3094"}'`
Sleep 300ms
Enter
Sleep 5s

Sleep 3s
